Package ides.api.plugin.layout

Class FSALayoutManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • ides.api.plugin.layout.FSALayoutManager
  • public class FSALayoutManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The manager of classes for the layout of FSAModels. Some layout classes are included with IDES.
    See Also:
    FSALayouter, registerLayouter(FSALayouter), getDefaultFSALayouter()

      • registerLayouter

        public void registerLayouter​(FSALayouter layouter)
        Register an FSALayouter with IDES. This class will become available for the layout of FSAModels.

        If a layouter with the same name has already been registered, the new layouter will replace it.

        Parameters:
        layouter - the layouter to be registered

      • getLayouter

        public FSALayouter getLayouter​(java.lang.String name)
        Retrieve the layouter with the given name. If no layouter with the given name has been registered, returns null.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the layouter
        Returns:
        the layouter with the given name; or null if no layouter with the given name has been registered
